<h2 id="Plugins_Settings">  Plugins Settings </h2>
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> You can enable/disable Plugins using the <a href="/bin/configure">configure</a> interface.
</li> <li> You can also disable installed plugins in individual webs/topics by defining the DISABLEDPLUGINS <a href="/bin/view/System/PreferenceSettings">preference setting</a> to be a list of plugins to disable e.g. <ul>
<li> Set DISABLEDPLUGINS = <a href="/bin/view/System/SpreadSheetPlugin">SpreadSheetPlugin</a>,EditTablePlugin
</li> <li> Currently, %DISABLEDPLUGINS% is set to ""
</li></ul> 
</li> <li> Currently activated Plugins: <a href="/bin/view/System/TWikiCompatibilityPlugin">TWikiCompatibilityPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/SpreadSheetPlugin">SpreadSheetPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/SlideShowPlugin">SlideShowPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/AttachContentPlugin">AttachContentPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/AutoTemplatePlugin">AutoTemplatePlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/AutoViewTemplatePlugin">AutoViewTemplatePlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/BibliographyPlugin">BibliographyPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/BookmakerPlugin">BookmakerPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/BreadCrumbsPlugin">BreadCrumbsPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/CaptchaPlugin">CaptchaPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/ClassificationPlugin">ClassificationPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/CommentPlugin">CommentPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/CompareRevisionsAddonPlugin">CompareRevisionsAddonPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/ConfigurePlugin">ConfigurePlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/DBCachePlugin">DBCachePlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/DiffPlugin">DiffPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/DigestPlugin">DigestPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/DocumentViewerPlugin">DocumentViewerPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/DpSyntaxHighlighterPlugin">DpSyntaxHighlighterPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/EditRowPlugin">EditRowPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/ExternalLinkPlugin">ExternalLinkPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/FilterPlugin">FilterPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/FlexFormPlugin">FlexFormPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/FlexWebListPlugin">FlexWebListPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/GraphvizPlugin">GraphvizPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/GridLayoutPlugin">GridLayoutPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/HistoryPlugin">HistoryPlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/HomePagePlugin">HomePagePlugin</a>, <a href="/bin/view/System/ImageGalleryPlugin">ImageGalleryPlugin</a>, <a href="/